verbose_text: Based on our recent study XREF_BIBR, a modest inhibition of intracellular ROS by the supplement with low dose antioxidants in medium likely contributes to decrease the DNA damage of human adult tissue stem cells and ES cells cultured in general CO 2 incubator (~ 20% O 2).
evidence: ROS by the supplement with low dose antioxidants in medium likely contributes to decrease the DNA damage
